opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 21st day of January, 2016, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED, and the Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
